formatted_address: 114 Middle Rd, #01-02 Lee Kai House, Singapore 188971
name: Ksing Karaoke 歌星

reviews.text: A very comfortable and cozy environment. Perfect for family and friends to gather together. The price is very cheap too, especially with their monthly promos! Will definitely come back again next time!

first time singing here and it definitely won’t be the last time. service was top notch and the room is big and cozy. sound quality is superb and the variety of songs are variousness. price is reasonable and they do open till late! they are currently having promotion so
do check ‘em out!

Had a excellent experience here. The staffs are super friendly and nice. Great quality sound for karaoke and clean rooms at affordable pricing. Can even 点歌 through the QR code on phone so don’t have to keep going over to the tv. Had a great time here, will definitely be back again!!

Always love coming here! Staff is always friendly and chill! Prices are pretty reasonable, even for drinks and sound system is pretty good. Love the fact they not only have a QR song system but it also works with Youtube so you can sing those niche songs you've always wanted to but could never find in any Karaoke catalogue.
A bit hidden but very nice k place. The place is clean, sound system is good, and price is very value.
